Its a nearly impossible idea. The equipment to run such a game is insanely expensive as is the bandwith needed.<br>
<br>
By open source, I'm assuming you mean it would be free also. In that case you are not going to get the quality of game makers working on it since they'd of course already be employeed by an mmorpg maker. <br>
